Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是罗兰德将校的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是从艾斯塔布尔村子里掳来的娈童？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳…琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大点声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塔尔罗姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你我的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了没 莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活命就给我拼死干活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想通了就快动手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}奈尔法皇国 旅店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝跳跃冲拳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}忘却碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能不要每次一登场就打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你碰伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被禽兽碰过就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我一碰就会怀孕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲莉丝这么跟你说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的啦 放心放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抓着我妹妹的手是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐骗幼女强奸怀孕什么的意思绝对没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近渐渐能从你那无表情中读出表情的我真是个天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了 伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路平安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我好想姐姐一路飞奔过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝…很强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是哄可爱的妹妹睡觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这也叫哄人睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候兄长就是这么哄我睡觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的一家子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子到底还是维尼特团子店的好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空吃东西还不来照顾下妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这能为她的将来负责吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝应该平安到达了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我的消息来得及送到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 这个好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早到晚团子团子团子个没完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝 你是来干嘛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？嗯…这个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝 拿了信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是席恩哥哥说要加急送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是很重要的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 呃…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的东西 不能丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩有没有跟你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他说龙突然消失了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那条莫名危险的龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要我们去调查其原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还说了什么很重要的话似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然很想去查查看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝 你去告诉席恩我们这就去查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于前几天 你们所报告的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面上长出龙的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那森林周围的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已被赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件遗物就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要再接近那森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}奈尔法皇国 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这喝茶应该挺风雅的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如放弃调查什么的麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来喝个茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是那条龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去调查原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有流血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以虽然死了这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却完全没有血腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边两位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你们是奈尔法的秘密监察官二人组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是来看传说中的龙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙能刺激作家的想象力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其来掳走了公主的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜错了别怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会搞出个勇者毅然反抗恶龙这种下三滥剧情来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以哥哥你的书永远都卖不出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是丈二和尚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 尸体都没有流血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 请你们解释一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 果然被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们杀的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们潜入那堡垒的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和二位一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说能理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也在找勇者遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才放任我们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们找到遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:09:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多亏破忌者部队的人们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料你们找到了遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还弃之不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是感激不尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们把看到龙的人全都杀掉灭口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避免得知遗物存在的人增加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要独占未知的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你们也要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集勇者遗物有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你们以为自己可以活下去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会问这种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实这问题也是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道你们是哪个国家派来的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿沉眠于大地中恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升身体能力的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西 无 阵 向阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西 无 阵 向阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…之处孕育光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 中途停止都能偷取吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再怎么被我的美貌迷得神魂颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于选这个时机来非礼我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还这么从容不迫的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来都是很从容的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多从容？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你没来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从容地死在刚才的攻击下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那镰刀很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是勇者遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看来是能将持有者的身体能力提升到变态的镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体不流一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及刚才的冰墙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那镰刀的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几次交锋之后 结冰的剑会变得越来越重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加周围气温也会下降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动会不够敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.19,0:11:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用火焰魔法掩护你制造空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去搞定那镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一试了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 作战方案敲定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那敢情好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是贵重的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要结晶化夺走才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你身为复写眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 比我还了解复写眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎一无所知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟他们连这“忘却碎片”都随手扔掉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“忘却碎片”？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就展示一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所丢弃的遗物的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是遗物的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“多尔艾利之剑鳞”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以根据使用者的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将攻击对象燃烧殆尽的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 地面是没有意志的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从地面长出来时是完全无害的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们好好尝尝遗物的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有闲工夫作壁上观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣 电光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是勇者遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 库的“艾尔克罗诺之镰”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“朵尔艾利之剑鳞”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及这“爱蕾米奥之簪”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕴藏着可将魔法无效化的神力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三件遗物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去没胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莱纳 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望一切都消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对莱纳做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不使其觉醒 就无法夺取复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼被人厌恶忌讳的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会失控破坏一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人称疯狂的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的杀戮者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在即是麻烦的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝…快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我…远点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的…我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人会死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这一切都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随心所欲地释放一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放 杀戮 所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认持有者崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对莱纳做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是恶魔失控 即将大肆破坏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会杀了他夺取结晶的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你也看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那点力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将在这“爱蕾米奥之簪”的神力下化为乌有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析存在 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 蝼蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯伊哥 还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的复写眼持有者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀吾？用那点力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区爱蕾米奥就想杀了吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匍匐在地的蝼蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 消失吧消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切皆为无
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归无吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 库
